task.summary: Default task
Added implementation of permuation of substring.
Added height and max width of a binary tree.
fixed unit tests. Still need to address Integer[] vs int[]; the conversion is being done on a shadow array which is not what we want.
Added unit teests for the sort algorithms. It's a little bit more comprehensive this time.
Added Node definition for list classes.
Test unit clean up.
Added test unit for merge sort
Added implementation of serializer and deserializer for binary tree.
Added two more codec implementing the serializer & deserializer for the binary tree.
New implemenation using LinkedList for serializing and deserializing the BST.
Moved the BST implemenation to *.tree* package.
added a missing file for the preorder implementation of bst.
Added string enecoder for serializing duplicate characters found in a given string. For example, 'aaabbfggd' should yield 'a3b2f1g2d1';
Migrated Queue implemention to array package since we are demonstrating use of Array as the implementation of a simple queue.
fixed implementation in sorts.
Simple cleanup
Added new support for math specific algorithms; particularly around bits manipulations.
Major refactoring of code to place logical placements of algorithms and data structures.
New text search implemenation based on naive, rabin-karp, knuthmorrisprate, and boyer-moore methods.
Imroved the search of min values in an array.
fixed some bit manipulation routines. Added examples of calculating the hammer weight of the decimal number.
Cleanup of binary conversion.
Added slew of algorithms; most for string permutations and binary search trees.
Added more solutions for string manipulations
Added hex and decimal conversion.
Added partition array of odd and even; also better support of linked list reversal.
Added LRUCache and better implementation of insertion-sort.
Added better implementation of queue using an array. Also needed to implement circular queue.
clean up singledlinkedlist
Added .idea/workspace.xml to .gitignore list
Added source linke to BFSNeighborList implementation.
Cleaned up tic-tac-toe game.
Minor clean up algorithms.
Delete old deprecated resources
Fixed some minor bugs with lca; returned null should have been return left or right depending on state of leaf.
Removed inappropriate comments for the isIdenticalBinaryTree.
Fixed bug with bst implementation.
Reworked the single linked list implementations.
Cleaned up single linked list; removed superfluous implementatino of reverse ( several implementation ); here we just choose the most elegant and readable code.
Implemented k sorted arrays and merge sorted arrays.
Aadded new implementation of k sorted arrays.
Reorganized the merged sorted arrays.
Simple Refactoring of Misnamed class.
New implementations of linked and sorting
Cleaned up implementation of find smallest pairs for k.
Clean up of algorithms for clarity
Removed redundant implement of some routines in singly linked list.
Added print utility to list class
Removed static reference to head reference and size. Each instance obviously needs it own private copy.
